A function to replace NA in the data frame by MAI::MAI() with random forest and single imputation.

Usage

impute_mai(missdf, ...)

Arguments

missdf

a data frame with missing values to be imputed containing features in columns and samples in rows.

...

other parameters of MAI::MAI() besides data_miss.

Value

A data.frame with imputed values by MAI::MAI().

Silent defaults

MCAR_algorithm is set to random_forest, MNAR_algorithm is set to single and verbose is set to FALSE.
